{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, BNC foot_3, short for the British National Corpus, encompasses 100M words of electronic text resources, covering spoken and written materials in British English.",
    "The second part is electronic text data constructed based on relevant written materials in various fields or topics.",
    "For example, FinGLM (MetaGLM, 2023) covers annual reports of some listed companies between 2019 and 2021.",
    "The data type belongs to language text materials in the financial domain.",
    "TigerBot-law (Chen et al, 2023c) includes legal regulations from 11 categories such as the Chinese Constitution and the Chinese Criminal Law, falling within the language text materials in the legal domain."
  ]
}